-	Evader & Monnok<br />
-	Trample<br />
-	Hutt Smooch<br />
-	Weapon Levitation<br />
-	Something Special Planned For Them (v)<br />
-	5 shields (Secret Plans, CHYBC, Weapon of a Sith, Resistance, Allegations of Corruption)<br />
<br />
